WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.960 --> 00:00:07.860
 Material gelatin tablets 4g, cranberry juice 200ml, fine sugar 10g, lemon juice 1 teaspoon, ice cubes 

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:18.140
 Pour the right amount of cold water into the pot and put the ice into it. 

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:29.560
 Geely tablets are separated into pieces in ice cubes 

00:00:29.560 --> 00:00:53.200
 Cranberry juice, fine sugar and lemon juice are placed in a pot until the sugar is melted 

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:23.100
 The soft gelatin tablets are picked up and the excess water is squeezed out. 

00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:34.340
 Put in hot juice and mix until melted 

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:54.620
 Pour completely into a suitable container 

00:02:00.780 --> 00:02:08.260
 Put it in the refrigerator and freeze it until it is completely solidified. 

